Package ch.epfl.lis.gnwgui

Implements different methods related to the Graphical User Interface (GUI).

See:
          Description

Class Summary
DynamicalModelElement Extends the generic network element to define dynamical models.
GenericElement Extends the interactive element iElement to represent network structures or dynamical models.
GnwConsoleHandler Handler of the GNW console loggers.
GnwConsoleSimpleFormatter This class defines a simple formatter to display log.
GnwConsoleWindow Window for the GNW console.
GnwGui Main class of the GeneNetWeaver GUI application.
GnwGuiSettings Offers global parameters (settings) and functions used by all classes of gnwgui package.
GraphSignature This class add a signature to a JUNG2 viewer (container).
GraphViewer Implements the actions linked to the graph visualization window.
HyperText Implements an interactive hypertext link.
IODialog This class is used to handle open/save dialogs.
IONetwork Implements all the methods to load/save networks from/to files.
Main  
NetworkGraph Implements a graph visualization using the JUNG library.
NetworkManager Extends a iDesktop to display open, bin and network icons.
Options Allows the user to choice one of the several process available applicable on a network structure or dynamical model.
Rename This dialog is used to rename a network.
SearchBox Implements of a text search box.
Simulation This dialog handles all the simulations parameters of steady-states and time-series experiments.
SplashScreen Splash screen of GeneNetWeaver.
StructureElement Extends the generic network element to define network structures.
SubnetExtraction This dialog allows to extract subnetworks from a source network.
 

Package ch.epfl.lis.gnwgui Description

Implements different methods related to the Graphical User Interface (GUI).

Package Specification

Compatible with the Java versions 1.5+.
